		    <title id="i2127381"
             outputclass="H304"
             xtrf="Grey"
             class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">532.904</ph> Determining payment due dates.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <p otherprops="Body"
            audience="GSAR"
            outputclass="Grey_Body"
            xtrf="Grey"
            class="- topic/p ">Payment due dates for construction contracts are addressed at FAR 32.904(d). The following procedures apply to construction and building service contracts:</p>
			      <ol id="d569e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li otherprops="abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d564e20"
                  outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The amount of final payment must include, as appropriate, deductions to cover any of the following:</p>
					          <ol id="d569e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li otherprops="123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d564e30"
                        outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Liquidated damages for late completion.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d564e39"
                        outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Liquidated damages for labor violations.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d564e48"
                        outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Amounts withheld for improper payment of labor wages.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d564e57"
                        outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The amount of unilateral change orders covering defects and omissions.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d564e66"
                        outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The agreed-upon dollar amount in a Deficiency Report, which is included in all applicable Operation and Maintenance (O&amp;M) service contracts.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d564e77"
                  outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             When the contract is for the performance of building services, the contracting officer shall include the clause at <xref href="GSAM-i1873639.dita#i1873639"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">552.232-72</xref>, Final Payment Under Building Services Contracts.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
